high_descs: Turn around and face the counter by the stove on your right.
Take the fork from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter on your right.
Place the fork in the cup on the counter in front of you.
Take the cup with the fork in it from the counter in front of you.
Turn around then right again and face the table on your right.
Place the cup with the fork in it on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter on the right, left of the stove.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Bring the fork over to the left.
Put the fork in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with fork on the counter.
Turn around, bring the mug with fork to the far side of the table on the right, turn to face the table.
Put the mug with fork on the table in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a fork in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the kitchen table, then hang left and go to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the fork on the counter behind the salt shaker.
Side step to the left of the counter to be center with a coffee cup.
Place the fork into the coffee cup with the tines up.
Pick up the coffee up from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the other end of kitchen. Slide between the edge of the table and the wall.
Place the coffee cup with the fork in front of the green apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a cup and place it in on the kitchen table.
